Rating: 4
I was looking for a recipe to use some white zinfandel that someone brought to me. (It's not my kind of wine for drinking) . Clearly the flavors of this dressing are bold. Too bold for a white zin. I cooked the garlic and only used the green tops of the onion, and used greek yoghurt instead of mayo. I'm not sure it's fair to review the recipe since I made so many changes. But it was so good. I had to share.

